Interface WeightAndMeasurementCustomized

All Superinterfaces:
ObservableUnit, ObservableUnitCustom, WeightAndMeasurement
All Known Implementing Classes:
Miscellaneous
public interface WeightAndMeasurementCustomized
extends WeightAndMeasurement, ObservableUnitCustom

The intention behind this interface is to model weights and measurement not fitting into one of the other units. It is thought to be a placeholder.
